snippet: The stalled baseball market is waiting for outfielder Josh Hamilton and starter Zack Greinke to sign so that teams can move on with other options.
abstract: Tyler Kepner On Baseball column notes that winter meetings ended without any significant trades or movement, stalled in part because teams are waiting to find out where star outfielder Josh Hamilton will play.
lead_paragraph: The stalled baseball market is waiting for outfielder Josh Hamilton and starter Zack Greinke to sign so that teams can move on with other options.

headline.seo: Baseball Meetings End Without Any Major Deals
